    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pat the <strong>tilapia fillets</strong> dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Gently add the <strong>tilapia</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 3-4 min or until the tilapia is cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
