      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, chop the<strong> parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Stir most of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) carefully through the cooked stew – this is your<strong> Mediterranean tilapia stew</strong></p>",
